				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224031" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;" >GreenWolf</a></span> <span class="odate time_1510073666 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Nov 2017 16:54</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3627815">
									

<p>Just making a note that I went through and added the handful of new goi-format articles that were posted but not added to this hub (<a href="/sounds-of-silver">Sounds of Silver</a> by Taffeta and <a href="/the-dark-web-dke79-o2rg5-4jlw6">'The Dark Web' (DKE79/O2RG5/4JLW6)</a> by DrChandra). I also took the time to go ahead and fix a handful of alphabetization errors that have cropped up.</p>
<p>If you're writing a goi-format, please please please remember to add it to this page (and properly alphabetized too).</p>

