			<div class="content" id="post-content-3715939">
									

<p>With approval from Taffeta, I've updated this page to automate the listings of GOI Formats. Any format with the proper goi-format tag (_prometheus for PL formats, _unusual-incidents-unit for UIU formats, etc&#8230;) will now appear here automatically and properly sorted. There's a slight hit to page load time as a result, but nothing intolerable. If it gets to a point where there's enough formats that it's slowing down the page significantly, the modules can be replaced with a bot-updated listing, as is currently done with the tales pages.</p>

